From: Jason Gunthorpe <jgg@nvidia.com>
Date: Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:11:11 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] iommufd: Require drivers to supply the cache_invalidate_user
 ops
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.10.10
Git-commit: a11dda723c6493bb1853bbc61c093377f96e2d47

[ Upstream commit a11dda723c6493bb1853bbc61c093377f96e2d47 ]

