bisection aid.

Fixes: 8c6eabae3807 ("iommufd: Add IOMMU_HWPT_INVALIDATE")
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/0-v1-e153859bd707+61-iommufd_check_ops_jgg@nvidia.com
